    <string name="about_privacy_title">Data Transparency &amp; Privacy</string>
    <string name="about_privacy_body">This app prioritizes your privacy. All financial data (transactions, balances, and history) is stored locally on your device using an encrypted database.\n\n1. Notification Processing:\nNotifications are processed locally on-device. Only relevant text content required for transaction analysis is sent to AI.\n\n2. No Cloud Storage:\nNo personal financial data is stored on any server. Uninstalling the app removes all local data unless exported by the user.\n\n3. AI Assistance:\nAI is used solely as a supportive tool for transaction detection and classification. Personalization rules remain stored on-device.</string>
